by redirecting the output of the <OLINK TARGETDOC="REFMAN1M" TARGETPTR="PRTVTOC-1M"><CITEREFENTRY>
<REFENTRYTITLE>prtvtoc</REFENTRYTITLE>
<MANVOLNUM>1M</MANVOLNUM>
</CITEREFENTRY></OLINK> command to a file.</PARA>
