of Solaris software on multiple disks.</PARA>
<ITEMIZEDLIST>
<LISTITEM>
<PARA>If no, stop. You are finished.</PARA>
</LISTITEM>
<LISTITEM>
<PARA>If yes, concatenate the single&ndash;disk configuration files
and save the output in a new file.</PARA>
