c0t3d0s0, c0t3d0s1, c0t4d0s0. <LITERAL>disksize</LITERAL> sets <ENVAR>SI_DISKLIST</ENVAR>, <ENVAR>SI_DISKSIZES</ENVAR>, <ENVAR>SI_NUMDISKS</ENVAR>, and <ENVAR>SI_TOTALDISK</ENVAR>.</PARA>
</ENTRY>
